story.title: Drive-Thru
story.storyDescription: Ted: Hey do you want anything from the burger joint?

messages.text: Hey do you want anything from the burger joint?
No. That place is disgusting. Why do you keep going to that drive-thru?
It’s going to make you sick. You may even die from it one day.
Yeah yeah…hold on I’m pulling up, need to order
There’s always a line at this place but I pulled right up
Then the voice on the speaker was muffled and just said ‘What do you want?’
That’s strange. Bad customer service today I guess
Yeah not the usually polite girl who runs the drive-thru
Maybe they’re giving her a break from that awful place
Hold, pulling up to the pay window
Can’t believe you actually pay for that garbage
And I could see under a little bit. The register was open and things were strewn everywhere. No one was there though.
OMG what if they got robbed
Then why would the robber be taking order in the drive-thru? For my extra $5?
Hold on, pulling up to the next window, maybe it’s a shift change
And there was black stuff all over the window
Yeah, some kind of think paste, I dunno
OK, time for you to go
No I’m going inside to check it out
I have to. What if people are hurt inside?
uhh…I just called 911 and got a busy signal??
OK, I’m at the door, heading in
Looks like a lot of people were in the middle of their meals
Sounds like there is some action in the back
Yeah like one of the machines crunching stuff, I dunno
I don’t think you should go back there
The thing they use to grill sandwiches. There was a goddamn severed head!
Wait I hear something coming from the freezer in the back
Exactly, someone needs to stop him if folks are still here
Someone is banging on the door and screaming
Yeah I’m going to let them out
She just ran out of the store
I mean she didn’t even look at me
She was covered in blood. She just ran.
Wow. Something terrible happened. I’m trying the police again.
They’re saying 5-10 minutes. A lot of calls tonight they said. From fast food joints.
It was weird, the 911 operator ask me if I was pranking her.
So this is happening all over town then? How?
I don’t know but I think you should leave
Let the cops take care of it
But I care about these people
Let me look around some more
There’s a door locked here in the back
Please don’t open it. Can you hear anyone inside?
But I don’t have the key. Let me look around for it
There was a man standing with his back to me
With the people who used to work in the store
Just standing at the machine, processing their bodies
OMG did he hear or see you open the door?
I think I’m going to be sick…
Of course you just saw something terrible
As I was walking around looking, I got hungry
There were some freshly made burgers on the counter
So I took a few bites of one
Thought it tasted a little funny
Did the guy say anything to you at all?
As I left the shop, I thought I heard him yell…
